                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Allow 1 in-game day to pass and go to the herb gatherer's house in",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(236, 229, 216)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Qiaoying Village",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ".",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "items": [
                    [
                      {
                        "content": [
                          {
                            "text": "Interact with \"Pharmacy's Amelioration\" on the stairs behind the house.",
                            "type": "text"
                          }
                        ],
                        "type": "paragraph"
                      },
                      {
                        "content": [
                          {
                            "text": "\"Pharmacy's Amelioration\": \"A few leagues to the east of",
                            "type": "text"
                          },
                          {
                            "styles": [
                              "color:rgb(236, 229, 216)"
                            ],
                            "text": "Mt. Xuanlian",
                            "type": "text"
                          },
                          {
                            "text": "is an earthen raft, that can float even without water. On the raft is a strange grass, with large leaves and roots like young children, its name is Xiangjun. Its sound is like that of an infant, and it travels with the raft, smiling when it sees people, and can ward off evil.\"",
                            "type": "text"
                          }
                        ],
                        "type": "paragraph"
                      }
                    ],
                    [
                      {
                        "content": [
                          {
                            "text": "Interact with the fully bloomed flowers in the yard to receive a 4-Star Soulscent Bloom (",
                            "type": "text"
                          },
                          {
                            "amount": 0,
                            "display_style": "text",
                            "ep_id": 2076,
                            "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/reliquary/Echoes of an Offering/flower_of_life_icon.png",
                            "name": "Echoes of an Offering",
                            "type": "custom_entry"
                          },
                          {
                            "text": ") artifact.",
                            "type": "text"
                          }
                        ],
